* Continuous Jobs\n(Always-On)
** Configuration
***_ Trigger type: Continuous
***_ Task retry mode: On failure / Never
** Exponential Backoff
***_ Activates after consecutive failures
***_ Wait period increases with failures
***_ Max wait set by system
***_ Resets after successful run
** Task Retry Mode
***_ On failure: retry task before new run
***_ Never: only retry at job level
** Monitoring
***_ Job details panel
***_ Consecutive failure count
***_ Success threshold period
***_ Time to next retry
** Note
***_ No task dependencies in continuous mode
@endmindmap
